[I] Library and command-line tools for configuring and getting information on paper sizes

[T] The libpaper package enables users to indicate their preferred paper size,
[T] provides the paper utility to find the user's preferred default paper size
[T] and give information about known sizes, and specifies system-wide and
[T] per-user paper size catalogues.

[U] https://github.com/rrthomas/libpaper

[A] Reuben Thomas <rrt@sc3d.org>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

